text: Parlor Tricks is an album from former Phish percussionist Marc Daubert, who was in Phish from the fall of 1984 to early 1985. The album features all original compositions with Daubert on guitar and vocals. ==Track listing== #Warm Up #Hips #Off The Record #So Wrong #F-5 #Library Lions #At The Ready #WMD #G-8 #Under The Rug #Whisper #The Void #Narcissus Category:2006 albums
